The paper deals with logic and languages over infinite pictures, which are a type of discrete structure. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Logic (cs.LO) or Discrete Mathematics (cs.DM) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper mentions subshifts of finite type and sofic subshifts, which are both topics in the field of Computational Complexity (cs.CC). The paper also discusses the Monadic Second Order (MSO) Hierarchy, which is a topic in Formal Languages and Automata Theory (cs.FL) and Information Theory (cs.IT). Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.LO and cs.DM, followed by cs.CC, cs.FL, and cs.IT.
